### Load a model into the active backend
POST http://localhost:7878/extensions/local-llm/models/mi_7c4b2d10/load HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Response 202
HTTP/1.1 202 Accepted
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "load_task_id": "ld_4e11a802",
    "progress_channel": "extension:local-llm:model:progress",
    "estimated_duration_seconds": 12
  },
  "error": null
}

### Read current load state (truth source — NEVER inferred by client)
GET http://localhost:7878/extensions/local-llm/backends/be_llamacpp/load-state HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Response 200 — model currently loaded
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "backend_id": "be_llamacpp",
    "loaded_model_id": "mi_7c4b2d10",
    "loaded_at": "2026-04-15T10:31:08Z",
    "ready": true
  },
  "error": null
}

### Response 200 — no model loaded (process ready, but nothing resident)
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "backend_id": "be_llamacpp",
    "loaded_model_id": null,
    "loaded_at": null,
    "ready": true
  },
  "error": null
}
